{"title":"把酒临风","authors":["李道莹"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":7,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"把酒临风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李道莹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公元1921年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马克思主义的光芒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照耀了沉睡的东方故园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"觉醒的龙的传人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举起真理的火炬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从嘉兴南湖开启了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理在胸英勇无畏的航船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事业的发达"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的幸福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"始知创业维艰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用马列主义、毛泽东思想指引"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千难万险只等闲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盼宏图大展"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事业代有伟人继"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邓小平理论挽狂澜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场“真理标准”的大讨论"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯一检验在实践"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驱散迷雾擦亮双眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“三中全会”正航向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"融入世界直面未来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让中华民族走进了春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国家繁荣事业昌盛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万民喜上眉尖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屹立世界民族之林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洲四海钦羡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有新时代的领路人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“三个代表”再谱新篇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘长风破万里浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创造更辉煌的明天"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}